<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.2.8">
<l>māvā yiṉaṅkam matiyā tukīṟi maḻaimā mutukuṉ ṟeṭuttā yartaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>kōvāy niraimēyt tulakuṇ ṭamāyaṉ kuraimā kaḻalkū ṭuṅkuṟip puṭaiyīr</l>
<l>mūvā yiranāṉ maṟaiyā ḷarnāḷum muṟaiyāl vaṇaṅka vaṇaṅkā yacōti</l>
<l>tēvā titēvaṉ tikaḻkiṉ ṟatillait tiruccit rakūṭam ceṉṟucēr miṉkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who have the intent, “We will reach the great rattling anklets of Māyaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">who consumed the world, having grazed the herd as king of the herders,</l>
<l>Taking up that great ancient hill [in] the rain, [and] splitting,</l>
<l rend="indent">without faltering, the mouth [and] body of a horse,”</l>
<l>Go and gather at Tiruccitrakūṭam in Tillai where shines</l>
<l rend="indent">the first god of gods, the light which became a divine being,</l>
<l>So that three-thousand experts in the four Vedas worship daily</l>
<l rend="indent">according to ritual.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
